⍝ Reduce.tc
⍝ ═════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: LO dyadic function
      ⍝ inv: ⍴Z ←→ ¯1↓⍴B
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ 0⌈¯1+⍴⍴B
